{"tid":2461484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台：59歲男子西貢失去知覺其後死亡　7日前接種復必泰","createTime":"2021-03-25T12:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:20:03.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5fff7e738adfd849cf05d324def161ffec6410e0","tid":2461484,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名在上周四接種過<strong>復必泰新冠疫苗</strong>的59歲男子，今日在西貢被遠足人士發現失去知覺，由政府飛行服務隊送往東區醫院，搶救無效證實死亡。本港累計有11宗接種疫苗其後死亡的個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署說，這名男子在設於彩虹道羽毛球中心的社區疫苗接種中心接種疫苗，接種後逗留在中心觀察期間，並沒有不適紀錄，個案將交由新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會，進行因果關係評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582604-20210325.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582604-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=b17f0257\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582604-20210325.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f2a3673a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582604-20210325.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4a9b97719ecd661cd87cf93c12dcd2d3f368689d","tid":2461484,"uid":59179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"點解話係作故仔"}]}